      "settings": {
        "text_width": "regular",
        "title": "",
        "content": "<h2>Why Shop for Your Barber and Salon Supplies with Hair & Beauty Kingdom?</h2><p>Founded in 2014, we are Australia's premier wholesaler of products and equipment for the hair and beauty supplies industry. We are recognised as a reliable stocking point because we supply the right brands, the finest products and a prompt and efficient  elivery service. Our warehouse features over 600 square feet of space, with more than 12,000 individually coded items on its shelves. </p><p>We believe that the industry requires high-quality products to support their line of work, so we pride ourselves on fulfilling this need every day. Working closely with you to ensure your demands are met, we continue to bridge the gap<br/>for affordable hair and beauty supplies and accessories online, without sacrificing quality.</p>",
