      "name": "Rich text",
      "settings": {
        "text_width": "regular",
        "title": "",
        "content": "<h2>Discover Massive Savings on Hair and Beauty Supplies When You Buy Online in AU or NZ</h2><p>With a commitment to accessibility, we ensure the convenience of easy online<br/>purchasing and unconditional trade prices, making an affordable range of stock available across Australia and New Zealand. Whether you own a busy salon or are a home hairdresser, we welcome you to purchase online or in-person at our warehouse showroom, where you can buy <a href=\"https://hairandbeautykingdom.com.au/collections/salon-furniture\">salon furniture</a>, <a href=\"https://hairandbeautykingdom.com.au/collections/hair-straightening-keratin-straightening-and-perming\">straighteners</a>, <a href=\"https://hairandbeautykingdom.com.au/collections/clipper-and-trimmer-accessories\">trimmers</a>, <a href=\"https://hairandbeautykingdom.com.au/collections/lashes-brows-accessories\">lashes</a> and experience exceptional customer service.</p><p>Are you ready to make a wholesale account with us? We look forward to supplying you with practical and affordable items that are ideal for your shop. <a href=\"https://hairandbeautykingdom.com.au/apps/wpdapp\">Fill out a registration form</a> and enjoy the many benefits of becoming a regular purchaser at our store.</p>",
        "button_text": "Contact Us",
        "button_link": "shopify://pages/contact-us"
      }
    }
